{"page_id": 53844, "slug": "Transformers_x_Evangelion", "title": "Transformers x Evangelion", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Transformers x Evangelion</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "\nTransformers x Evangelion is an official crossover of [[Transformers]] and Neon Genesis Evangelion with an toyline and story series<ref>https://comicsalliance.com/transformers-x-evangelion-optimus-eva-prime-action-figure</ref> <ref> http://www.zonebase.org/2017/10/transformers-mode-eva-chapters-1-4.html?m=1</ref>\n\n==Toy line==\nThere is as an toy of Optimus Prime with EVA colors and a NERV trailer, roller and a human operative\n[[File:Transformers x Evangelion Optimus Prime-Eva mode.jpeg]]\n===Transformers mode “EVA”===\n[[Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”|See: Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode EVA”]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Character List}}\n\n[[Category:Crossovers]]\n[[Category:Toys]]\n{{expand}}\n{{cleanup}}", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Transformers x Evangelion is an official crossover of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Transformers&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Transformers (page does not exist)\">Transformers</a> and Neon Genesis Evangelion with an toyline and story series<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Toy_line\">Toy line</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Transformers_x_Evangelion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Toy line\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There is as an toy of Optimus Prime with EVA colors and a NERV trailer, roller and a human operative\n<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Transformers_x_Evangelion_Optimus_Prime-Eva_mode.jpeg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/a/a8/Transformers_x_Evangelion_Optimus_Prime-Eva_mode.jpeg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" class=\"mw-file-element\" /></a></span>\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Transformers_mode_.E2.80.9CEVA.E2.80.9D\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transformers_mode_“EVA”\">Transformers mode “EVA”</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Transformers_x_Evangelion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Transformers mode “EVA”\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/Transformers_x_Evangelion:_Transformers_mode_%E2%80%9CEVA%E2%80%9D\" title=\"Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode “EVA”\">See: Transformers x Evangelion: Transformers mode EVA”</a>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Transformers_x_Evangelion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"https://comicsalliance.com/transformers-x-evangelion-optimus-eva-prime-action-figure\">https://comicsalliance.com/transformers-x-evangelion-optimus-eva-prime-action-figure</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.zonebase.org/2017/10/transformers-mode-eva-chapters-1-4.html?m=1\">http://www.zonebase.org/2017/