gi\" title=\"Dr. Katsuragi\">Dr. Katsuragi</a> | <a href=\"/Mr._Langley\" title=\"Mr. Langley\">Mr. Langley</a> | <a href=\"/Keel_Lorenz\" title=\"Keel Lorenz\">Keel Lorenz</a> | <a href=\"/Pen_Pen\" title=\"Pen Pen\">Pen Pen</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<td><b><a href=\"/Rebuild_of_Evangelion\" title=\"Rebuild of Evangelion\">Rebuild of Evangelion</a></b>:  <a href=\"/Asuka_Shikinami_Langley\" title=\"Asuka Shikinami Langley\">Asuka Shikinami Langley</a> | <a href=\"/Mari_Makinami_Illustrious\" title=\"Mari Makinami Illustrious\">Mari Makinami Illustrious</a> | <a href=\"/Sakura_Suzuhara\" title=\"Sakura Suzuhara\">Sakura Suzuhara</a> | <a href=\"/Ryoji_Kaji_(Jr)\" title=\"Ryoji Kaji (Jr)\">Ryoji Kaji (Jr)</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<td><b>Miscellaneous</b>: <a href=\"/Minor_Characters\" title=\"Minor Characters\">Minor Characters</a> | <a href=\"/Minor_Characters_(Rebuild)\" title=\"Minor Characters (Rebuild)\">Minor Characters (Rebuild)</a> | <a href=\"/Extracanonical_Characters\" title=\"Extracanonical Characters\">Extracanonical Characters</a> | <a href=\"/2015:_The_Last_Year_of_Ryohji_Kaji\" title=\"2015: The Last Year of Ryohji Kaji\">2015: The Last Year of Ryohji Kaji</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<td><b><a href=\"/Category:Theory_and_Analysis_of_Characters\" title=\"Category:Theory and Analysis of Characters\">Theory and Analysis</a></b>: <a href=\"/Character_Name_Origins\" title=\"Character Name Origins\">Name Origins</a> (<a href=\"/Warships_in_Evangelion\" title=\"Warships in Evangelion\">Warships</a>) | <a href=\"/Evangelion_Character_Designs\" title=\"Evangelion Character Designs\">Designs</a> | <a href=\"/Category:Relationships\" title=\"Category:Relationships\">Relationships</a> | <a href=\"/Category:Character_Profiles\" title=\"Category:Character Profiles\">Profiles</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br clear=\"all\" />\n</p>\n<table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseag